{"tid":2357019,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：立會因佢多個掣  李桂華亂吹政治冷知識（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-07T07:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T07:41:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eed1c326b214f3f16d95cc6330807dbf490462ba","tid":2357019,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/B6YIX4YYMFGEDNRXT55RWSCPHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FB6YIX4YYMFGEDNRXT55RWSCPHY%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z6Eelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=02db32bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FB6YIX4YYMFGEDNRXT55RWSCPHY%2F&h=6efe7b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/B6YIX4YYMFGEDNRXT55RWSCPHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：立會因佢多個掣 <br />\n李桂華亂吹政治冷知識（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BCEl2F1VNNdYPdA0L_tsVonNmoQ=/1200x858/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CF3O3P5JYFHIXKJYH36MQFHEW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBCEl2F1VNNdYPdA0L_tsVonNmoQ%3D%2F1200x858%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCF3O3P5JYFHIXKJYH36MQFHEW4.jpg&h=3faeb62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日政權對民主派初選一鋪過大清算，負責拉50幾人嘅國安處高級警司李桂華會見記者解說，搞個初選投票點樣變成「顛覆國家政權」罪。見李大導咁有信心，向傳媒解釋立法會點可以「顛覆國家政權」，八方以為佢一定好熟書啦，點知一聽之下，原來佢連基本嘅立法會工作、《基本法》內容都講錯晒，唔怪得黃浩銘同網民都話：「只要見李桂華有份出現，你就知道這件案件必會變為業餘、不認真，和像馬戲團。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃浩銘嘲似馬戲團<br />\n<br />\n警方記者會上，有記者問到搞初選點解係「非法手段」，李大導就話：「根據《基本法》73條，立法會嘅權力同義務係冇呢樣嘢。」先唔講法律冇寫嘅嘢點解就會變咗「非法」，既然要拋書包，《基本法》73條列明嘅係立法會嘅「職權」，而唔係「權力與義務」喎！李Sir係咪以為上緊小學常識課？<br />\n<br />\n佢之後又講到立法會議員對議案嘅否決權，話議員一係投贊成、一係反對、一係「無意見」。八方聽到呢度真係打咗個突，想問吓李桂華，根據立法會投票嘅基本常識，議員選擇只有贊成、反對、棄權，又或者缺席、不按投票掣，幾時多咗個掣叫「無意見」？就算佢唔睇立法會新聞，都睇吓全國人大投票啦，做問卷調查就話有得揀「無意見」啫。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華仲發表「揸車打劫論」，話今次可以比喻揸車係合法，但揸車目的係打劫就有問題。黃浩銘就喺記者會上鬧爆呢個神奇邏輯，恥笑有李桂華出現就真係會變馬戲團。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"d13ed6ad2a1332a04acfd8148239e64c79b06e25","tid":2357019,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"馬戲團堅professional㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那嗰啲賣藝行乞就差唔多"},{"pid":"cb4c439d1ac15c7253b7b9f527ed3ef3e620e5ae","tid":2357019,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d13ed6ad2a1332a04acfd8148239e64c79b06e25","tid":2357019,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"馬戲團堅professional㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那嗰啲賣藝行乞就差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"其實用馬戲團嚟形容荷蘭叻同李大導 根本就係侮辱緊馬戲團呢個行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43874ab4479757fefd63ca7ed03d22030c4ec59","tid":2357019,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"宣咗誓都仲係唔識基本法<br />\n對佢好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567301b8cd8faf0a92e5de5d5116d051c0a04cdb","tid":2357019,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"circus clown"}]}